import React from "react";
import Header from "./Header";

export default function Login(props) {
  return (
    <>
      <Header text={"Login"} path={"/login"} />
      <UserForm
        title={"Регистрация"}
        button={"Зарегестрироваться"}
        path={"/login"}
      >
        <input
          className="userForm__input userForm__input_type_username"
          id="userEmail"
          name="userEmail"
          type="email"
          placeholder="Email"
          required
          minLength="2"
          maxLength="40"
        />
        <input
          className="userForm__input userForm__input_type_password"
          id="password"
          name="password"
          type="text"
          placeholder="Пароль"
          required
          minLength="2"
          maxLength="200"
        />
      </UserForm>
    </>
  );
}
